该死,琪亚娜怎么会有巴比伦实验室的记忆?.Translation: Damn it, how does Kiana have memories of the Babylon Laboratory?

检测到大量死士出没!.Translation: Detected a large number of undead approaching!

准备迎战坚守到舱门关闭!.Translation: Prepare for battle; hold until the hatch closes!

舱门已成功关闭!.Translation: The hatch has been successfully closed!

检测到大量死士从后方接近中.......Translation: Detected a large number of undead approaching from behind......

该死!这些死士到底是从哪里来的?.Translation: Damn it! Where are these undead coming from?

是第二律者,她正向我们这边传送死士!.Translation: It's the Second Herrscher; she is sending undead our way!

该死,上面也有死士出现!.Translation: Damn it, there are undead appearing above too!

趁下一波攻击到来前,赶紧离开这里.Translation: Hurry and leave before the next wave of attacks comes!

门被锁住了,我们没有磁卡需要时间破解!.Translation: The door is locked, we don't have the key card; we need time to hack it!

闸门破解完成!.Translation: The gate has been hacked successfully!

这么高的崩坏能浓度是怎么回事!.Translation: What is with this high concentration of Herrscher energy!

快启动安全系统降低崩坏能浓度不然我们无法继续前进!.Translation: Quick, activate the safety system to lower the Herrscher energy concentration, or we can't proceed!

系统启动中.......崩坏能浓度正在下降.......Translation: System starting....... Herrscher energy concentration is decreasing......

崩坏能浓度已降低至安全水平!.Translation: Herrscher energy concentration has been reduced to safe levels!

ok!现在我们去把那个该死的崩坏炉关掉否者第二律者会更加强大.Translation: Ok! Now let's go shut down that damn Herrscher reactor, or the Second Herrscher will become even more powerful!

崩坏炉关闭程序启动中!.Translation: Herrscher reactor shutdown procedure is starting!

守住这里,直到崩坏炉彻底关闭!.Translation: Hold this position until the Herrscher reactor is completely shut down!

崩坏炉已关闭.Translation: The Herrscher reactor has been shut down.

检测到虚数空间波动大量死士接近中!.Translation: Detected fluctuations in the imaginary space; a large number of undead are approaching!

去控制中心调查一下是怎么回事!.Translation: Go to the control center and investigate what's going on!

守住!等待电梯到来!.Translation: Hold the position! Wait for the elevator to arrive!

里面就是控制中心了坚持到闸门破解完成!.Translation: Inside is the control center; hold on until the gate is hacked!

快利用控制台关闭闸门.Translation: Quick, use the console to close the gate!

闸门已关闭数据传输中.......Translation: The gate is closed; data transmission in progress......

该死!她发现我们了.Translation: Damn it! She has discovered us.

守住,等待数据传输完成.Translation: Hold the position, wait for the data transmission to complete.

守住这里!等待电梯到来.Translation: Hold this position! Wait for the elevator to arrive.

快撤!快撤!赶紧进电梯!.Translation: Quick retreat! Quick retreat! Get into the elevator!

上面被不知名的力量封锁了,正在尝试破解.Translation: The upper area is sealed by an unknown force; attempting to hack it.

快还击她是第二律者！.Translation: Quick, strike back! She is the Second Herrscher!
